name: orderInquiryAndUpdate

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged into 'Order Inquiry Update' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Inquiry & Reports,Logistics Reports,Order Inquiry & Update}

exception.message: Expected condition failed: waiting for visibility of element located by By.xpath: //div[@class = 'sidebar-menu-container'] (tried for 10 second(s) with 100 milliseconds interval)

testSteps.description: Then the 'Order Inquiry Update' page and its contents should be visible
When I set the 'Branch Plant' to '1MAN400'
When I set the 'Order Number' to '19042337'
When I click 'See More' button from first 'Inquiry Update' card
Then the 'Order Inquiry' search result should show up
When I clik the checkbox of the first order
Then the 'Update Order' modal should show up
